rComments: He's enthusiastic but material wise there is very little new stuff learned in this course. A lot of material is just common sense that is very obvious (there exist national differences, duh) or RSM100 all over again, which makes the course easy but boring. Need to write a lot for this course (4000-6000 word essays x2 + 8000 group) so be prepared.

Terry is an amazing prof and I would take his course again! The course materials for 490 is mostly at macro-level business. There will be two individual written cases, however, the professor is always available for help and is very very patient! You can also def learn tons of stuff from his lecture!

Very well structured class. Reflects on readings, but always has very relevant and interesting information.  Take his International Business and Strategy classes, you won't regret it. One of the few classes that I really enjoyed.
